{"tid":415680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［司法不干涉立法］市民申覆核「一地兩檢」方案被駁回","createTime":"2017-09-27T07:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T08:23:50.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d8f47233f1709992a4995ebe12dba8c316478220","tid":415680,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:32:51.000Z","msg":"政府公布高鐵「一地兩檢」方案後，先後有5名市民入稟司法覆核，指「一地兩檢」涉內地關員在西九龍車站範圍執法，有違憲之嫌。高院上周就是否批出司法覆核許可開庭，聽取申請人和政府的陳詞後，今午（27日）頒下裁決，並拒絕頒下覆核許可，意即法庭不會排期就申請正式聆訊，但申請人仍有樣就法官的這個決定提上訴。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/122001/-一地兩檢-市民欲挑戰政策涉違憲-法庭拒頒覆核許可#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F122001%2F-%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%AC%B2%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2-%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E6%8B%92%E9%A0%92%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E8%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D1&d=B1ym5ZOO8g6sZ79udEQl19tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f950e3ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/122001/-一地兩檢-市民欲挑戰政策涉違憲-法庭拒頒覆核許可#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1</a>"},{"pid":"f63a852d025083318d272f406e1131b75616ae79","tid":415680,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"唔開官名有咩討論價值"},{"pid":"5a9f07c03024d77e9ca532e712b33aaefada0de9","tid":415680,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:47:20.000Z","msg":"香港人：嘩！香港好有法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d94c4fcc3f69b1cc60af91a7bc2581fc85e23a","tid":415680,"uid":37584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:48:00.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"657b09a0078c5362f8008a62a5635f6802154ad7","tid":415680,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔開官名有咩討論價值</blockquote><br />\n周家明法官，講完你又知佢係邊個咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"